text: Tsotne () is a Georgian masculine given name that may refer to: *Tsotne Bakuria (born 1971), Georgian politician *Tsotne Dadiani (died c. 1260), Georgian nobleman *Tsotne Machavariani (born 1997), Georgian sport shooter *Tsotne Rogava (born 1993), Ukrainian Muay Thai kickboxer Category:Georgian masculine given names
title: Tsotne
